Download the library and include the `html2pdf.bundle.min.js` file in your extension folder. Update the `manifest.json` file to include this file in the content scripts:
```json
"content_scripts": [
  {
    "matches": ["*://*/*"],
    "js": ["html2pdf.bundle.min.js", "content.js"]
  }
]
```
Now, update the `content.js` file to use the html2pdf.js library for converting the webpage to a PDF:
